## Playwright Test Results

### Test 1: Homepage Hero
- **PASS** Homepage loaded — HTTP 200
- **PASS** Video background element (`<video>`) present
- **PASS** Page title: "Cornerstone Construction Co. | Built to Last"
- **PASS** Hero heading found: "BUILT TO LAST."
- **PASS** Navigation links: Home, Services, Projects, Contact (both desktop and mobile nav)

### Test 2: Services / Pricing Page
- **PASS** Services page loaded — HTTP 200
- **PASS** Pricing content detected (dollar signs / pricing language present)
- **PASS** 54 service/pricing card elements found (3 services x tiers + detail rows)

### Test 3: Projects Gallery
- **PASS** Projects page loaded — HTTP 200
- **PASS** 56 project elements found (gallery cards + detail items)
- **PASS** 5 filter buttons present (All, Residential, Commercial, Excavation, Featured)

### Test 4: Contact Form
- **PASS** Contact page loaded — HTTP 200
- **PASS** Contact form element present
- **PASS** Name, email, and message fields all fillable
- **WARN** No inline confirmation text after form submit — expected for a static demo; form validation runs client-side and a real submit would need a backend endpoint

### Test 5: In-Page Navigation
- **PASS** Clicking Services nav link from homepage navigates to services.html correctly

### Test 6: Portfolio Route (work-samples SPA)
- **PASS** `/work-samples/construction-company-website` resolves via GH Pages 404.html SPA redirect
- **PASS** Demo iframe present with `src: https://michaelwegter.com/demos/construction-company-website/`

### Test 7: Same-Origin Resource Check (all 4 pages)
- **PASS** Zero same-origin 404s across all four pages (homepage, services, projects, contact)
- Note: One transient console error was observed in the first test run but did not reproduce in any subsequent pass. It was not from `michaelwegter.com` resources (likely a third-party CDN/font preconnect timing issue). All local demo assets resolve correctly.

### Test 8: WorkSamples Registry
- **PASS** `src/data/workSamples.js` contains entry with slug `construction-company-website`, title "Cornerstone Construction Co.", status "live", correct `href` using `import.meta.env.BASE_URL + "demos/construction-company-website/"`

